    "content": "<p>Let's talk about the good stuff, the bonuses! Who doesn't love a good bonus? In Fortune Falcon Wild Respins, there are two symbols that trigger special features: the golden egg falcon and the palace. The golden egg falcon fills up one of the three slots at the top of the screen when it appears on reel four. Once all three slots are filled, the free spins bonus feature is activated. And who doesn't love free spins? During these free spins, a giant golden egg appears on three of the five reels. This egg will behave as a wild symbol, so every time a winning combination is formed, you'll hear the sound of breaking eggs and see gold coins falling from them - now that's an egg-cellent feature. </p>

