{
  "headline": "<h2>GAMEPLAY</h2>",
  "content": "<p>Oh, the thrill of the spinning reels! Fortune Falcon Wild Respins has a grid with 5 reels and 3 rows, featuring 30 fixed pay lines. It's no surprise that a winning combination is formed by aligning at least 3 identical symbols from left to right - after all, we've seen this in countless slot games before. But what makes Fortune Falcon stand out is the betting range - as low as €0.01 per line and as high as €100.</p>

