  <p>Oh, and did we mention the theoretical return to player (RTP) is 94.02%? While it may be slightly lower than other slots, it's still nothing to scoff at. Fortune Falcon is a game suitable for both less experienced players and those who have been around the block a few times. Give it a whirl and see what fortune has in store for you!</p>"
}

